I really enjoyed this simple salad and will definitely make again. I've been looking for a super fast dressing to compliment a mixed greens and egg salad, and this is perfect! East, fast, and delicious! I didn't use goat cheese; just the mixed greens, bacon, and over-easy eggs. I also added some thinly sliced red onions and I really liked the added layer of flavor. Will make again!

