Rating: 4
This is my husband's & my favorite salad -- fast, easy and delicious! Especially good for a light meal now that summer is here (in Arizona, at least). I just made it for the third time for houseguests and they raved too. I opted to cook an extra couple slices of bacon and to double the amount of dressing, but others might prefer "drier" greens.

